[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     31[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mScope each role to the specific resource ARNs it touches. The permissions above are fine for learning and will fail any serious IAM review. In production, each component (device-ingest Lambda, ehr-event-ingest Lambda, enrollment-handler Lambda, event-normalizer Lambda, feature-engine Lambda, scoring-orchestrator Lambda, explanation-builder Lambda, worklist-builder Lambda, intervention-capture Lambda, outcome-capture Lambda, retraining Step Functions workflow) gets its own role with the minimum permissions for its job.[K
