FAIRWarning line 659: **Amazon API Gateway and AWS AppSync for the privacy-office case management UI.** The privacy office's case queue UI consumes data through AppSync (when GraphQL flexibility is needed for the case-detail views) or API Gateway (for simpler integrations). When the organization uses an existing privacy-monitoring vendor (Protenus, FairWarning, etc.), the integration is API-driven and the UI is the vendor's; the AWS-native components feed it through the integration layer.
